### Get all countries (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/countries

### Get all countries (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/countries?page=2&limit=10

### Get country by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/countries/3

### Create country
POST http://localhost:5000/api/countries HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "New test country",
  "code": "TST"
}

### Update country
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/countries HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": 44,
  "title": "Updated country",
  "code": "UPD"
}

### Delete country
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/countries/44 HTTP/1.1
